it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface GUIModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface GUIModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'GUI Model'. Modello di un'applicazione

    The following features are supported:

    • Structure
    • Beahviors
    • Cod Prodotto
    • Cod Componente
    • Versione Prodotto
    • Versione Componente
    • Typedefs
    • App Data Defs
    • Portale
    • Security Model
    • Ext Security Model
    • Target Platform
    • Activation Model
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getGUIModel()
